          "text": "Reactive adenitis\nBacterial\nlymphadenitis\nTuberculous lymphadenitis\nCellulitis\nCat-scratch disease\nParotitis\nSuppurative parotitis\nViral parotitis\nLymphangitis\nToxoplasmosis\nTularemia\nViral disease\nHIV-AIDS\nCytomegalovirus\nEpstein-Barr Virus\nFungal disease\nReactive adenitis",
