          "text": "Malignancy\nLymphoma\nMetastatic cancer\nRheumatologic Disease\nKawasaki Disease\nSystemic lupus erythematosus\nSarcoidosis\nJuvenile Idiopathic Arthritis\nLangerhans Cell Histiocytosis\nCutaneous Lesions:\nBacillary angiomatosis\nPurpura\nHematomas\nAngiomas\nDermatofibromas\nNevi\nDrug reaction\nPhenytoin\nor\nCarbamazepine\nPostvaccination\nSarcoidosis\nSalivary gland diagnoses",
