        "Acute": {
          "text": "Reactive\nlymphadenopathy\n- most common\nViral\nURI\nEBV\nCMV\nStrep\n/\nstaph\nHIV\nToxoplasmosis\nBartonella henselae\n- kitten or flea exposure\nTuberculous lymphadenitis\n(scrofula)\nDescending infections from oral cavity\nLudwig's angina\nSialoadenitis\n(can also be chronic)\nTrauma\n-related\nHematoma\nPseudoaneurysm or AV fistula",
          "tables": []
        },
